source.name: Defense Logistics Agency Video Podcasts
source.description: The Defense Logistics Agency (DLA) is the Department of Defense's largest logistics combat support agency, providing worldwide logistics support in both peacetime and wartime to the military services as well as several civilian agencies and foreign countries. DLA Podcasts makes it easy for anyone with a Web site, blog or social networking page to learn about the DLA.  You can scroll through our gallery and select videos to view on-line, or you can subscribe to our podcast feed.
